	<!-- TEXT  -->
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Keep It Holy</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_HELP">
			<Text>Its those three chaps from the peninsula again, Your Munificence. Something about a star being seen in the sky over the City. The usual.[NEWLINE]They await you in the antechamber, planning their route home.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The Natural Wonder permenantly yields +1 [ICON_PEACE] Faith, [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism and [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Allow the first sect {2_InstantYield}. A Free Church is constructed in the City, it yields +3 [ICON_PEACE] Faith.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Allow the second sect {2_InstantYield}. A Free Mosque is constructed in the City, it yields +3 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Allow the third sect {2_InstantYield}. A Free Monastery is constructed in the City, and you receive a copy of [ICON_RES_WINE] Wine.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>*The three men claim Mt Sinai poses the sign of God, and that an event of great importance shall soon come to pass*[NEWLINE]I am very important, and I am coming to pass. I'd say they're spot on. Thank them and send them back to their... wherever it is they live.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*The first man regales you with the story of how God reached down from the heavens and blessed man with knowledge atop Mt Sinai*[NEWLINE]Clearly a Church would be an appropriate way to show respect to this holy place.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*The second man insists that the first man's story is ever so slightly off, and that a burning bush was somehow involved*[NEWLINE]If this is the case then perhaps a Mosque would be more appropriate.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_MT_SINAI_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*The third man is not having any of the other two, and claims it is actually the desert around Mt Sinai which is where the important events took place*[NEWLINE]Then let the faithful cultivate the valley, to the glory of God!</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
